        <mxCell id="z0eYjY46S8jfoElOQu6q-8" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF9C4;strokeColor=#FBC02D;fontSize=9;" value="Notes&#xa;- Centralized Basement Core - Minimal upstairs hardware&#xa;- Starlink as WAN2 failover (future)&#xa;- Wazuh for asset monitoring + vulnerability scanning&#xa;- All IoT strictly isolated (egress-only)&#xa;- Layers: 1. Current State (faded) 2. Future Rack Layout 3. Logical VLAN Flow&#xa;- Fiber from outside → Basement Rack (FIOS ONT)&#xa;- All LAN originates from Managed Switch → Patch Panel → drops&#xa;- Archer A7 repurposed as additional WAP (AP Mode)&#xa;- pfSense/OPNsense: 4+ NICs (WAN1 FIOS from ONT, WAN2 Starlink, LAN trunk)" vertex="1">
